Dialogue: 0,0:00:-01.00,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:38.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yuba" "Erumalu" "Nanohana" "Katorea"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years have passed since\Na single drop of rain fell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.88,0:01:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the kingdom of oases.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.51,0:01:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing hope beyond turmoil,\Nthe people took up weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The burning land is now\Nenveloped by a sad bellowing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a mighty swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.89,0:01:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, to reach Yuba,\Nwhere the rebel army is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy's group set into the desert...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...where numerous, unimaginable\Nhardships fell upon them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Enter the Desert Pirates!\NThe Men Who Live Freely"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.14,0:02:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So hot... Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Zoro. This heat\Nis too much for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.18,0:02:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act polite. It's stifling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! How far did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That side of you is wonderful too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is much easier\Nthanks to you, Lashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But will the others be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.87,0:02:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll just follow the footprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsunami!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A tsunami's coming!\N--What's going on, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it wasn't such\Na good idea after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What wasn't a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him not to, but he said he\Nwas so thirsty he couldn't stand it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he chomped down on some\Ncactus growing back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cactus?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those round things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Those are bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are mezcal cacti! They're\Nused to make hallucination drugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna drown!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Bring it on, if you dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat all of you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.86,0:03:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tranquilizer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:04:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Do you see Nami's group?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn. We're completely\Nseparated from them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And their footprints are disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I haven't\Nseen Ace for a while, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did he disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he got separated from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh! What a troublesome big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the ones who got separated!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--All because of you!\N--Quit acting so carefree!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hear something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aah! It's--!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami and Vivi've been caught!\NOh, and the camel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey! Luffy!\N--Don't be rash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Let's go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Give-Me-Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.58,0:05:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out of strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.86,0:06:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I just hear something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so thirsty I misjudged...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, do you have any water?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you didn't come to save us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only came to get water.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help, Luffy-san!\NLashes is about to be eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing's edible?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, the Barbar Sand Pirates, have a saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from friends, nothing alive\Nin the desert can't be eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll even eat stuff off the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll make you sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a funny pipsqueak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're funny too! Well, let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.27,0:07:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Barbarossa, captain of\Nthe Barbar Sand Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.51,0:07:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, was it? I'm sorry for our\Nrough treatment of your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that we're all so hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not for you to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Captain! We don't have any\Nwood at all to repair our main mast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without a main mast,\Nwe won't have enough thrust!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Yeah! What're we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.37,0:07:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't do something,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're going to die like dogs\Nin the middle of this desert!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We're gonna die like dogs!\N--Huh?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The Barbar Sand Pirates are gonna die!\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We sand pirates are born\Nin sand pirate ships,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.72,0:08:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll die in sand pirate ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abandoning our ship is unthinkable!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's right! We'll die in our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll die like dogs in our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was fate, this was fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We sand pirates will never do\Nanything to defy the flow of sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't say I didn't warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is timber at the Meriyasu Oasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?! I'll rush there real quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:09:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the sands've changed lately.\NIt's dangerous for outsiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm responsible for it! I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?! You will?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring back wood with this sand-sled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say this is more of\Na canoe than a sled...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zaba and Rasa will show you\Nto the Meriyasu Oasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Rasa?\N--Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.50,0:09:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rasa is our ship's finest sand-sledder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sand-sled can carry two people.\NWhat'll you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now! Quit saying\Nbaseless things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll probably be demanding work.\NWant me to go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That was cool, Rasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:10:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The others seem to be outsiders...\Nbut you're from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! How could she tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have some\Nexperience with a sand-sled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-chan can't do\Nanything that dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So these go on top of\Nthe sand? How does it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pilot the sled.\NI did this once long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not too different from a ship.\NThis goes like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't waste your strength\Ndoing stupid things!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can rest there, Luffy-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's see. I believe\Nthis goes like this and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:10:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh. Let's go, Zaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Rasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.67,0:11:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we borrow this,\Ncan't we reach Yuba right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to control sand-sleds.\NIt's not something easily mastered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how come you can control it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to practice with a sand-sled\NI received when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what should we do while we wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to eat the camel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Yay! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't sound like a joke to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.11,0:11:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! What's the big idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rasa! That's--!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:12:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Vivi! We're getting\Npulled in more and more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quicksand! If we get\Nswallowed into the sand,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll never come back out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rasa. Wasn't that going too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If luck's on her side,\Nshe'll make it through alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You know that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. As if I'd ever forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You alright, Vivi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in trouble if we don't do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.94,0:12:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi! Duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:13:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite how he seems, you can\Nalways count on Luffy in a pinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But what concerns me\Nmore is the desert's fickleness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The desert's fickleness?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The desert is honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A slight change in weather or\Npeople's hearts will change it greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A change in people's hearts?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! It's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Turn to starboard! Hurry!\N--Battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna get in my way, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--There are so many of them!\N--Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Desert bandits! Pests who're\Nalways desperately fighting us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conflict seems imminent these days!\NThat has them on edge, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you can't move!\NYou're finally ours today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men! Don't let a single\None of them leave alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.13,0:14:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our pleasure! Our pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:15:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, a pub?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The desert has pit us together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will the desert choose us,\Nthe Barbar Pirates, or you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's let the desert\Ndecide our fate in battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! Fool! The desert'd never choose you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Grand Dung Beetle!\N--There's a Grand Dung Beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Grand Dung Beetle?\N--Say what now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.73,0:15:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Desert bugs that haul giant balls of dung!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No less than 100 people a year\Nare squished by their rolling dung!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! It's headed right for our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:16:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.06,0:16:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, guests...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll let you off easy this time!\NYour lives are spared for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That deserves a\Nwarm shower of applause.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rasa! Don't you think\Nyou went a little too far?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--They're not following!\N--That's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she won't come\Nhowever much we wait,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:17:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's just the level of a person she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.44,0:17:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We caught up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.56,0:17:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This oasis is completely buried in sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was once a flourishing city, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people of this city gave me\Na small sand-sled as a memento.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a very long time ago, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stopped by here once with my father
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when he was traveling around the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:18:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, the king told us,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If anything happens to this oasis,\NI will come rushing to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kingdom won't ignore any voice,\Nno matter how small."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, this oasis was\Nburied in sand and abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every last person in town left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I stayed behind\Nand waited for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believed in you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.35,0:18:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the king never came. Nor you, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because similar incidents\Nwere happening all over the country
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the king was busy every\Nday trying to combat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear your excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:19:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I waited all alone in the\Nmiddle of this vast desert!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, I couldn't\Ndifferentiate between dawn and dusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.65,0:19:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the time Barbarossa took me in,\NI couldn't feel anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not even the midday scorching heat\Nor the freezing cold after sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that I was even alive baffled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, inside my head,\Nthe king's words continue to ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.34,0:19:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I don't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things were so difficult,\Nso what exactly was I waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what kept me going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hate? Anger? Or inexistent hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.21,0:20:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry for making you wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.20,0:20:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure ran off in a hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's too bad we didn't get\Nto swipe any of their food or water.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sand pirates sure have it tough, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything living in this\Ndesert has it the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, I used to feel this\Ndesert belonged to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.36,0:20:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I think about it now,\NI feel like that's a bit conceited.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:21:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, I've come to think that\Nit might not belong to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That we're able to live freely\Nbecause it belongs to no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the sea is the same way?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's something you'll have\Nto find out for yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the adventurers\NI dreamed of when I was a child
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I continue on to the ends of emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:22:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I scoop up my hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.09,0:22:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the sand and time\Nthat spills from them
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.70,0:22:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,show me that this is\Nwhat I was born to do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.71,0:22:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue swimming\Nat a near-tumbling speed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.79,0:22:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we wash up someday\Non a white sandy beach
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.56,0:22:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no one knows about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.25,0:22:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Say, Luffy. Where's your brother?\N--Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.95,0:23:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's worse at directions\Nthan this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.85,0:23:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Who're you\Ntalking about, Pervy Cook?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.12,0:23:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else is there besides you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.22,0:23:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I got food and water!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.76,0:23:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Big brother! How?!\N--Got it from the rebel army!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.43,0:23:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.83,0:23:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.36,0:23:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"False Fortitude!\NCamu, Rebel Soldier at Heart!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.97,0:23:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
